  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for tiff",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for tiff fixes the following issues\n\n- CVE-2026-12912: heap-based buffer overflow when processing crafted PixarLog-compressed TIFF image (bsc#1269779).\n- CVE-2026-36849: denial of service when processing a a crafted TIFF file containing a large SamplesPerPixel tag value\n  (bsc#1268434).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
